            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='28'>Supply Chain Delay Root Cause Analysis</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='5484' id='35' type-v2='text' w='95075' x='2542' y='6884'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#555555' fontsize='20' italic='true'>Identifying operational bottlenecks across carriers, ports, products, and service levels</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='26838' id='36' type-v2='text' w='26370' x='73312' y='28238'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Delay Rate: </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#cf0b09' fontsize='11'>48.37% </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>of analyzed orders</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Highest Risk Carrier: </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#cf0b09' fontsize='11'>V444_0</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Worst Service Level: </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#cf0b09' fontsize='11'>DTP</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Top Delayed Products: Delay rates exceed 75%</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Most delays occur within</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#cf0b09' fontsize='11'> 0–3 days</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Estimated Delay Cost: </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#cf0b09' fontsize='11'>₹2.88 lakh</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='5368' id='37' type-v2='text' w='9770' x='73550' y='23687'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14' italic='true'>Key Insights</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='4434' id='38' type-v2='text' w='45115' x='477' y='94399'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>Dataset: </run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>Brunel Supply Chain Logistics Dataset          </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>Tools: </run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>Python, Pandas, NumPy, Tableau</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='6301' id='40' type-v2='text' w='16918' x='73709' y='55659'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14' italic='true'>Recommendations</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='36523' id='41' type-v2='text' w='25258' x='73392' y='61727'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Shift volume toward lower-delay carriers to improve overall delivery performance.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Improve service-level execution for DTP shipments through targeted process audits.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Focus inventory and logistics planning on high-delay product categories.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Establish delay-monitoring dashboards for real-time operational visibility.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Use carrier and service-level performance metrics during vendor negotiations.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>• Implement predictive risk scoring to identify potentially delayed shipments early.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
